Missing:  
107 (ends 7)  
113 (3)  
131 (1)  
139 (9)  
149 (9)  
157 (7)  
163 (3)  
167 (7)  
173 (3)  
181 (1)  
193 (3)

Our included:  
101 (1), 103 (3), 109 (9), 127 (7), 137 (7), 151 (1), 179 (9), 191 (1), 197 (7), 199 (9)

So included: last digits: 1,3,9,7,7,1,9,1,7,9  
→ digits: 1 appears 3 times, 3 once, 7 three times, 9 three times.

Missing include all last digits too.

